Arithmetic Expressions

    Operator Precedence
        Precedence of adjacent operators

    Operator Associativity
        Either left to right or right to left

    Conditional Expressions
        average = (count == 0) ? 0 : sum / count;

    Comma Expressions
        average = a+b,b //evaluates as a+b; average = b
        IN GENERAL: (expr1, expr2, expr3, ..., exprn) preforms exprs in order 1..n and evaulates to exprn

    
